00:01:51.545 --> 00:01:53.413 align:middle line:90%
>>Be here now.

00:01:58.085 --> 00:01:58.952 align:middle line:90%
Don't anticipate.

00:02:03.690 --> 00:02:08.895 align:middle line:84%
Don't yearn for
things of the past.

00:02:15.135 --> 00:02:22.976 align:middle line:84%
Let the past go
with forgiveness.

00:02:31.651 --> 00:02:37.257 align:middle line:84%
And let the future go
with no anticipation.

00:02:43.930 --> 00:02:53.305 align:middle line:84%
Each of us contains a
being that doesn't die

00:02:53.305 --> 00:02:55.609 align:middle line:90%
and a being that does die.

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:11.825 align:middle line:84%
Everything must change,
except the soul.

00:03:36.716 --> 00:03:43.523 align:middle line:84%
Your preparation
for dying is done

00:03:43.523 --> 00:03:50.464 align:middle line:84%
by identifying with
your soul, not your ego.

00:04:01.174 --> 00:04:04.878 align:middle line:90%
Identify with your soul now.

00:04:16.456 --> 00:04:26.733 align:middle line:84%
Realms other than the
one we are meeting on,

00:04:26.733 --> 00:04:33.473 align:middle line:84%
realms where we meet the
souls that we have known

00:04:33.473 --> 00:04:38.111 align:middle line:90%
in the past as just souls.

00:04:51.024 --> 00:05:01.234 align:middle line:84%
We won't meet them in their
clothing of mother or father

00:05:01.234 --> 00:05:03.036 align:middle line:90%
or uncle or aunt.

00:05:15.215 --> 00:05:28.361 align:middle line:84%
Then are sensual planes,
planes with color,

00:05:28.361 --> 00:05:48.682 align:middle line:84%
music, planes
which have no form.

00:05:53.420 --> 00:05:57.857 align:middle line:84%
This plane is where
all of it starts.

00:06:01.861 --> 00:06:10.170 align:middle line:84%
This plane is the womb,
the beginning of things.

00:06:15.141 --> 00:06:22.315 align:middle line:84%
This plane is ecstatic, is
the ultimate creativity.

00:06:36.296 --> 00:06:44.371 align:middle line:84%
Dying is the most
important moment

00:06:44.371 --> 00:06:46.940 align:middle line:90%
that exists in any incarnation.

00:06:51.745 --> 00:07:02.055 align:middle line:84%
It is important that you not be
so overwhelmed by the processes

00:07:02.055 --> 00:07:02.722 align:middle line:90%
of dying.

00:07:10.397 --> 00:07:27.681 align:middle line:84%
I wish you a process for dying
that doesn't overwhelm you.

00:07:34.587 --> 00:07:46.132 align:middle line:84%
I wish you a moment of dying
that you can be conscious of.

00:07:52.872 --> 00:08:10.824 align:middle line:84%
I wish you a future incarnation
in a plane of incredible light.